The following targets should subclass `JvmTarget`, not `ExportableJvmLibrary`, because as codegen targets they are not actually exportable - their synthetic derivatives are. This prevents publishing artifacts of these target types.

```
class JaxWsLibrary(ExportableJvmLibrary):
class JavaWireLibrary(ExportableJvmLibrary):
```

